data.text:
İlkay Gündoğan is 33 years old (Oct 24, 1990), 180 cm tall and plays for Barcelona.

İlkay Gündoğan prefers to play with right foot. His jersey number is 22.

Barcelona is playing their next match on Aug 17, 2024, 7:30:00 PM UTC against Valencia - Barcelona in LaLiga.

If İlkay Gündoğan is going to be in Barcelona lineup, it will be confirmed on Sofascore one hour before the match starts.

If İlkay Gündoğan plays you will also be able to follow his live Sofascore rating, statistics and heatmap. İlkay Gündoğan football player profile displays all matches and competitions with statistics for all the matches İlkay Gündoğan played in. Most important stats for each competition, including average Sofascore rating, matches played, goals, assists, cards and other relevant data are also displayed.
